        <title>OpenAI在网络安全工具中的非常规应用：逆向工程与代码审查</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/p/openai%E5%9C%A8%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E9%80%86%E5%90%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5/</link>
